; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">sent =
shareholders a proxy statement</a> explaining that it wanted to dissolve an=
d give them the money back=C2=A0and asking them to vote. Then it held a sha=
