nk" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text=
-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color=
: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">got about 1=
.29 million votes</a>, still not nearly enough.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin=
: 16px 0;">So it=C2=A0is trying some nonsense. The <a href=3D"https://link.=
