<div id=3D"footnote-1" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[1] A nuance here is that the big exchange ope=
rators tend to run multiple venues, and if you are starting a second exchan=
ge your goal is probably not to displace the first: Your goal is to offer s=
ome different trading mechanics or fee structure or listing standards, so t=
hat your trading or listing customers can get an optimized experience.</p>
</div>
<div id=3D"footnote-2" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[2] I am guessing at that one. But <a href=3D"=
